What this fork adds on top of upstream caveman
----------------------------------------------

A model-aware token-cost optimizer layer (the "Fable 5 / Opus 4.8 optimizer"),
living mostly under:

    src/core/         deterministic compression, protected spans, secret scan,
                      markdown sectioning, token counting, model pricing, cache
    src/commands/     caveman-compress, caveman-bench, caveman-doctor, caveman-config
    src/hooks/        adaptive micro-injection policy + Fable/Opus-aware stats
    src/mcp-servers/  caveman-shrink framing/transform hardening
    evals/            budgeted online + offline eval harness, fixtures, reports
    docs/OPTIMIZER.md the optimizer's full design + capabilities doc

See docs/OPTIMIZER.md for what the optimizer does and how it works, and
docs/fable5.md for the Fable 5 / Opus 4.8 model notes.

